              <div class="author__content">
          <p>Abass S. Kamara is District Surveillance Data Officer for the Sierra Leone Ministry of Health and Sanitation and Kambia District Health Management Team. He is also a Research Assistant for the Anthropology of Emergency Vaccine Deployment (AViD).</p>
        </div>
          </div>
      <div class="author__main">
