        <h3>Luisa Enria</h3>
      </div>
              <div class="author__content">
          <p>Luisa Enria is Assistant Professor at the London School of Hygiene &amp;amp; Tropical Medicine. She is the Sierra Leone case study lead for AViD and currently holds a UKRI Fellowship titled ‘Crisis of Confidence: The Politics of Evidence and (Mis)trust in Epidemic Preparedness’.</p>
